#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an10.82"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.82:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.82:0.2"
msgid "9. Theravagga "
msgstr "9. Senior Mendicants "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.82:0.3"
msgid "82. Ānandasutta "
msgstr "82. With Ānanda "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an10.82:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Ānanda went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one side. The Buddha said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an10.82:2.1"
msgid "“So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘assaddho samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. (1) "
msgstr "“Ānanda, it’s not possible for a faithless mendicant to achieve growth, improvement, or maturity in this teaching and training. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an10.82:3.1"
msgid "So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘dussīlo samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. (2) "
msgstr "It’s not possible for a mendicant who is unethical … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an10.82:4.1"
msgid "So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘appassuto samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. (3) "
msgstr "uneducated … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.153, sc5
msgctxt "an10.82:5.1"
msgid "So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘dubbaco samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. (4) "
msgstr "hard to admonish … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an10.82:6.1"
msgid "So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘pāpamitto samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. (5) "
msgstr "with bad friends … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an10.82:7.1"
msgid "So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘kusīto samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. (6) "
msgstr "lazy … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an10.82:8.1"
msgid "So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘muṭṭhassati samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. (7) "
msgstr "unmindful … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an10.82:9.1"
msgid "So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘asantuṭṭho samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. (8) "
msgstr "lacking contentment … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "an10.82:10.1"
msgid "So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘pāpiccho samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. (9) "
msgstr "of bad desires … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "an10.82:11.1"
msgid "So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘micchādiṭṭhiko samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. (10) "
msgstr "of wrong view to achieve growth, improvement, or maturity in this teaching and training. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc12
msgctxt "an10.82:12.1"
msgid "So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘imehi dasahi dhammehi samannāgato imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr "It’s not possible for a mendicant with these ten qualities to achieve growth, improvement, or maturity in this teaching and training. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc13
msgctxt "an10.82:13.1"
msgid "So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘saddho samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. (1) "
msgstr "It is possible for a faithful mendicant to achieve growth, improvement, or maturity in this teaching and training. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc14
msgctxt "an10.82:14.1"
msgid "So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘sīlavā samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. (2) "
msgstr "It is possible for a mendicant who is ethical … "

# NOTE: I’m not sure if BB overlooked sutadhara or if he didn’t think it needed translating.
#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc15
msgctxt "an10.82:15.1"
msgid "So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘bahussuto sutadharo samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. (3) "
msgstr "a learned memorizer … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc16
msgctxt "an10.82:16.1"
msgid "So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘suvaco samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. (4) "
msgstr "easy to admonish … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc17
msgctxt "an10.82:17.1"
msgid "So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘kalyāṇamitto samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. (5) "
msgstr "with good friends … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc18
msgctxt "an10.82:18.1"
msgid "So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘āraddhavīriyo samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. (6) "
msgstr "energetic … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.154, sc19
msgctxt "an10.82:19.1"
msgid "So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘upaṭṭhitassati samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. (7) "
msgstr "mindful … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc20
msgctxt "an10.82:20.1"
msgid "So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘santuṭṭho samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. (8) "
msgstr "contented … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc21
msgctxt "an10.82:21.1"
msgid "So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘appiccho samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. (9) "
msgstr "of few desires … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc22
msgctxt "an10.82:22.1"
msgid "So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘sammādiṭṭhiko samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. (10) "
msgstr "of right view to achieve growth, improvement, or maturity in this teaching and training. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc23
msgctxt "an10.82:23.1"
msgid "So vatānanda, bhikkhu ‘imehi dasahi dhammehi samannāgato imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjatī”ti. "
msgstr "It is possible for a mendicant with these ten qualities to achieve growth, improvement, or maturity in this teaching and training.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.82:23.2"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
